Here is the desired Java function that matches the provided pseudocode:

```java
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        calculate();
    }

    public static void calculate() {
        for (int n = 2; n <= 10; n++) {
            int result = n * 2;
            System.out.println(result);
        }
    }
}
