pip install sympy
```

The `sp.solve` method will return the roots of the equation. These roots can be real or complex numbers.

Please note that the script may not always find a perfect solution especially for higher order polynomials due to some numerical issues or when there is no real root to the equation. The results from the script should always be verified for correctness.
