I am trying to query sentences with specific keywords. I am using python btw
my implementation:

words = ['word1', 'word2']
#dummy set of words, words are fetched dynamically

queryList = sum([[{'title':{'$regex':w, '$options':'i'}}, {'media':{'$regex':w, '$options':'i'}}] for w in words], [])
#creating a list of all queries for passing into an $or operation
query = {'$or':queryList}
#preparing the query 

posts = (postsCollection.find(query).sort('points', -1))


it is returning me `Regular expression is invalid`
sometimes it doesn't give me a specific set of words and it gives an error with another particular set of words
